`8Keywords``   : Deathblow
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * deathblow <target>

 Deathblow lands a powerful hit on the target, but has the nasty side effect of
reducing your hp. Kill or be killed, very much so. Be very wary of it.

